how to initialize npm 
1- npm init

how to import file in ES module
1- go to package.json
2- add "type" : "module"

how to install module through npm 
1- npm i/install module/package name

how to observe changes in file
--> for this we can use nodemon package globally, we can also install this package locally but normally we need this feature across different project
so we are installing it globally
1- npm install nodemon -global

how to exit from nodemon observable envoirnment
--> ctrl+c